            <div n="r" type="textpart">
               <p>
                  <milestone n="1" unit="line"/>Heras to Taphes my sister, many greetings. Above all I pray you and your family are in good health. 
You should know that I have written to you twice and you have not written to me in answer to any of the letters. 
<milestone n="7" unit="line"/>Receive from - - sandy-coloured sandals and a hair shirt and ... of a fruitcake and ... and dates ... that you make the account (?) ... you will write to me. 
Goodbye 
<milestone n="20" rend="break" unit="line"/>To Heras my sister, very many greetings. Above all I pray you are in good health. I write you, until I come up, to thank you for the clothing. 
I do homage to the god on behalf of you. 
               </p>
            </div>
            <div n="v" type="textpart">
               <p>
                  <milestone n="28" unit="line"/>To Philadelphia, give to my sister Heras. 
                  <note>Translation: P.Leid.Inst. 1 42</note>
               </p>
